item.title: Impact of Education and Technology Investments on AI Competitiveness in Global Economy
item.description: This project explores the critical role of artificial intelligence (AI) in shaping countries' economic competitiveness, emphasizing key factors influencing national AI capabilities. The study employs cluster analysis, comparative analysis, and predictive models to address key research questions.
